      <title>在安知鱼主题中增加来访者侧边栏</title>
      <link href="/posts/37773/"/>
      <url>/posts/37773/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>成果：<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/11/18/Ew8Ufr5pnYSB7Me.png" alt=" 2024-11-17 220538.png"><br>首先，参考<a href="https://blog.mc-sep.top/">mc-sep的博客</a>。<br>我发现他的网站上居然有来访者标签耶！！！！<br>如果我也搞一个那不就可以装逼了？<img no-lazy class="inline" src="https://weilegetu.com/images/202202/5fe8810751e436202371dba5fcf95c81.gif" style="height:60px;"/></p><p>首先，搜索引擎搜到了<a href="https://blog.qjqq.cn/posts/834f.html">青桔气球的文章</a><br>但是，那位博主使用的主题是solutide，我的是anzhiyu-c,那咋整呢？看了其他的几篇文章，有些我又看不懂。<br>在我心如死灰之际，我找到了这篇文章：<a href="https://blog.wfqyys.cn/archives/149html/hexo-sider">YYSのblog</a>，估计很久没有整理了，已经看不下去了，我看的是博客源代码，从中得到了灵感，便这样写：</p><ol><li>首先先在source/_data/ 目录下新建一个widget.yml文件，写上这几行代码:</li></ol><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">top:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">class_name:</span> <span class="string">guest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">id_name:</span> <span class="string">guest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">来访者</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">icon:</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-wifi</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">html:</span> <span class="string">&lt;div</span> <span class="string">id=&quot;welcome-info&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
