      <title>秦始皇最新力作：fuclaude部署使用指南</title>
      <link href="/posts/21712/"/>
      <url>/posts/21712/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我是一个喜欢<s>搞事</s>上网冲浪的男孩</p><p>最近，我发现了之前的<a href="https://github.com/wozulong">秦始皇wozulong</a>居然又在搓玩具了，fuclaude,意义我就不说了，字面意思。</p><p>因为国内不能直接访问claude ai,所以就出现了这个项目</p><ol><li><p>准备工作：</p><ul><li>steam++(现已改名为<a href="https://steampp.net/">watt toolkit</a>)</li><li>可以上网的浏览器</li><li>一个huggingface账号</li><li>一个cloudflare账号</li></ul></li><li><p>食用方法：</p><ol><li><p>打开watt toolkit，点上github加速。</p><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/f8c6d44808a2ba94b30c9.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/f8c6d44808a2ba94b30c9.png"></p></li><li><p>打开<a href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/wangxiaowang/fuclaude">这个链接</a>，点击右上角三个点，然后点击duplicate this space，信息填一下，静待一会儿，等到像下图一样，有Running的绿字，就代表成功了</p><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/db52d26249b6b59ec2e5d.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/db52d26249b6b59ec2e5d.png"></p></li><li><p>复制有圈的这行链接，每个人的不一样，也可以复制我的:<strong>wangxiaowang-fuclaude.hf.space</strong></p></li></ol><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/303a2b14dcb707f2748fc.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/303a2b14dcb707f2748fc.png"></p><p>d. 打开<a href="https://dash.cloudflare.com/">cloudflare</a>,没有账号的注册一下,注意哈，可能要等好久，实在不行就开个梯子吧。</p><p>创建一个新的worker，名字为fuclaude。</p><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/2f019635502e553924709.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/2f019635502e553924709.png"></p><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/c8eadd3bdc1af92336524.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/c8eadd3bdc1af92336524.png"></p><p>点击编辑代码</p><p><img src="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/eb33ea51840cdf040ba09.png" alt="https://image.wxiaow.us.kg/file/eb33ea51840cdf040ba09.png"></p><p>在里面填上</p> <figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">addEventListener</span>(</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&quot;fetch&quot;</span>,<span class="function"><span class="params">event</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">let</span> url=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title function_">URL</span>(event.<span class="property">request</span>.<span class="property">url</span>);</span><br><span class="line">     url.<span class="property">hostname</span>=<span class="string">&quot;wangxiaowang-fuclaude.hf.space&quot;</span>; <span class="comment">// 修改成自己的huggingface复制下来的地址</span></span><br><span class="line">     url.<span class="property">protocol</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;https&#x27;</span>; </span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">let</span> request=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Request</span>(url,event.<span class="property">request</span>);</span><br><span class="line">     event. <span class="title function_">respondWith</span>(</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(request)</span><br><span class="line">     )</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后再点击部署，绑定一下域名就ok了。建议白嫖党申请us.kg后缀域名,不建议申请cloudns域名,详见视频<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1by411B7Ko/?spm_id_from=333.976.0.0&amp;vd_source=9b7ef618693297e7c889951b2210fb89">2024最新免费域名教程，可托管CF，零失败率，解决所有坑点。</a> 里面也有怎么绑定域名的方法，建议康康</p><p>如果你都不想搞，那可以用始皇的demo网站:<a href="https://demo.fuclaude.com/">https://demo.fuclaude.com/</a> ，注册一个就行了。</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
